What you need to know:

Born and raised in Stockport, just six miles (10 kilometres) from the club's Etihad Stadium, Foden is the homegrown hero among a star-studded international squad bankrolled by the Abu Dhabi owners.The club that he first started training with as a six-year-old was very different. City had only recently returned to the Premier League after at one stage slipping down to English football's third tier.